title: Unemployment in India reaches 42-year high under Modi government, says AAP
description:
Unemployment in India reaches 42-year high under Modi government, says AAP The AAP's Rajya Sabha MP Sanjay Singh said that the prices of fuel and medicines have gone up considerably under Modi's rule. He also criticised the Agniveer scheme, saying that it has betrayed youngsters.
